== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
電影《[[銀翼殺手|-{zh-hk:2020; zh-tw:銀翼殺手; zh-cn:银翼杀手;}-]]》（1982年）續集於1999年開始發展。{{link-en|史都華·海澤丁|Stuart Hazeldine}}曾根據《{{link-en|銀翼殺手2：人類邊緣|Blade Runner 2: The Edge of Human}}》而撰寫續集，其改編電影命名為《''Blade Runner Down''》；不過，後來因小說版權的問題而被擱置<ref name="sequels">{{cite | url=http://www.mybladerunner.com/faq/1-8-are-there-any-sequels-i-heard-rumours/| title=The Blade Runner FAQ: Are there any sequels? I heard rumours .. | publisher=My Blade Runner | accessdate=2011-07-27| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028150147/http://www.mybladerunner.com/faq/1-8-are-there-any-sequels-i-heard-rumours/| archivedate=2012-10-28}}</ref>。第一部電影的導演[[雷利·史考特|雷利·史考特]]考慮開發續集，且暫定名為《''Metropolis''》，並在[[聖地牙哥國際漫畫展|聖地牙哥國際漫畫展]]上表達了自己對續集的興趣<ref name="sequels" /><ref>{{cite | url=http://www.thedigitalbits.com/site_archive/mytwocentsa140.html | title=My Two Cents | accessdate=2007-12-17 | publisher=The Digital Bits, Inc. | last1=Hunt | first1=Bill }}</ref>。2008年驚悚電影《[[鷹眼_(電影)|鷹眼]]》的編劇之一崔維斯·懷特與製片人{{link-en|巴特·約金|Bud Yorkin}}打算合作開發續集。幾年後，他的同事約翰·格倫在2008年前離開了該計畫，他表示該劇本將會探討非洲殖民地的特性，以及泰瑞公司在創始人死亡後所發生的事件<ref>{{cite | author=Sciretta, Peter | title=Exclusive: Screenwriter Travis Wright Responds to Blade Runner 2 Story | work=/Film | date=2008-10-06 | url=http://www.slashfilm.com/2008/10/06/exclusive-screenwriter-travis-wright-responds-to-blade-runner-2-story/ | accessdate=2011-07-27| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628200406/http://www.slashfilm.com/2008/10/06/exclusive-screenwriter-travis-wright-responds-to-blade-runner-2-story/ | archivedate=2010-06-28 }}</ref>。

2009年6月，《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》報導，雷利·史考特和他的弟弟[[東尼·史考特|東尼·史考特]]正在製作一部《-{zh-hk:2020; zh-tw:銀翼殺手; zh-cn:银翼杀手;}-》的前傳《''Purefold''》。該前傳被計劃為一系列5至10分鐘的短片，預計會以[[網路劇|網路劇]]或電視劇的形式推出。由於版權問題，使該系列不能與1982年電影的角色或事件有所關連<ref>{{cite|last=Stone |first=Brad |url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/06/04/web-series-tied-to-blade-runner-is-in-the-works |title=Web Series Tied to 'Blade Runner' Is In the Works|publisher=New York Times |date= 2009-06-04|accessdate=2011-07-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223044740/http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/06/04/web-series-tied-to-blade-runner-is-in-the-works/|archivedate=2014-02-23}}</ref>。2010年2月7日，由於資金問題，《''Purefold''》的製作已終止<ref>{{cite|url=http://www.ag8.com/ |title=Ag8 |accessdate=2011-12-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209225218/http://www.ag8.com/|archivedate=2014-02-09}}</ref>。2011年3月4日，{{link-en|io9|io9}}報導，巴特·約金正在開發一部新的《-{zh-hk:2020; zh-tw:銀翼殺手; zh-cn:银翼杀手;}-》電影<ref>{{cite|url=http://io9.com/#!5774950/a-warner-bros+financed-production-company-buying-the-rights-to-do-a-blade-runner-sequel-or-prequel |work={{link-en|io9|io9}} |publisher=Gawker Media |accessdate=2011-07-27 |date=2011-03-04 |first=Charlie Jane |last=Anders |title=''Blade Runner'' Sequel (or Prequel) in Development Now|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512085957/http://io9.com/ |archivedate=2014-05-12 }}</ref>。且還有報導說，[[克里斯多福·諾蘭|克里斯多福·諾蘭]]是該片的最佳導演人選<ref>{{cite|author=Orange, B. Alan|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/christopher-nolan-wanted-for-blade-runner-sequel-or-prequel |title=Christopher Nolan Wanted for Blade Runner Sequel or Prequel |publisher=MovieWeb.com |date=2011-03-04 |accessdate=2011-05-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104213322/http://www.movieweb.com/news/christopher-nolan-wanted-for-blade-runner-sequel-or-prequel|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref>。

2011年8月18日，宣布，雷利·史考特將執導一部新的《-{zh-hk:2020; zh-tw:銀翼殺手; zh-cn:银翼杀手;}-》電影，但不會在2013年前開始進行。製片人{{link-en|安德魯·科索夫|Andrew Kosove}}指出，前集的演員[[哈里遜·福特|哈里遜·福特]]不大可能會參與其中<ref>{{cite|last=Fleming |first=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/08/ridley-scott-ready-to-direct-new-version-of-seminal-sci-fi-film-blade-runner/|title=Ridley Scott To Direct New 'Blade Runner' Installment For Alcon Entertainment |publisher=deadline.com |date=2011-08-18 |accessdate=2011-08-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418103232/http://www.deadline.com/2011/08/ridley-scott-ready-to-direct-new-version-of-seminal-sci-fi-film-blade-runner/|archivedate=2014-04-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-14586762 |title=Ridley Scott to direct new Blade Runner film|publisher=BBC|date=2011-08-19|accessdate=2011-08-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420033805/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-14586762|archivedate=2014-04-20}}</ref>。史考特透露，該片「可能是一部續集」，但沒有以前的演員，而且他想找一名「可能能幫助[他]」的編劇<ref>{{cite|url=https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/11/04/ridley-scott-says-he%E2%80%99ll-direct-%E2%80%98blade-runner%E2%80%99-sequel/|author=Chai, Barbara|title=Ridley Scott Says He'll Direct 'Blade Runner' Sequel|publisher=Speakeasy|date=2011-11-04|accessdate=2011-11-06}}</ref>。2012年2月和10月，科索夫和史考特都表示，續集仍在發展中，而福特則不太有望能回歸演出<ref>{{cite|author=Vejvoda, Jim|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2012/02/07/harrison-ford-in-blade-runner-2 |title=Harrison Ford in Blade Runner 2?|publisher=ign.com|date=2012-02-06|accessdate=2012-02-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite |last=Sullivan |first=Kevin P. |title=Ridley Scott Gives 'Prometheus 2' And 'Blade Runner 2' Updates |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2012/10/12/prometheus-2-blade-runner-2-updates/ |work=MTV Movies Blog |accessdate=2012-10-13 |date=2012-10-12 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6JF334klm?url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2012/10/12/prometheus-2-blade-runner-2-updates/ |archivedate=2013-08-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

史考特於2014年11月表示，他不會執導該片，而僅是製片人，並預計於2014年底或2015年底開始製作，福特的角色只會出現在續集的「第三幕」中<ref>{{cite web|author1=Jacob Kastrenakes|title=Ridley Scott won't direct 'Blade Runner' sequel|url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/11/25/7286991/blade-runner-2-wont-be-directed-by-ridley-scott|website=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media, Inc|accessdate=2014-11-26|date=2014-11-25}}</ref>。2015年2月26日，續集確認由《[[私法爭鋒|私法爭鋒]]》（2013年）的導演[[丹尼·維勒納夫|丹尼·維勒納夫]]來執導，福特也會回歸演出瑞克·戴克一角，而前集的編劇{{link-en|漢普敦·芬奇|Hampton Fancher}}也會再度撰寫其劇本；該片預計將於2016年中開始製作<ref>{{cite | author=Joseph, Matt | title=Blade Runner Sequel Confirmed, Harrison Ford To Return | work=We Got This Covered | date=2015 | url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/blade-runner-sequel-confirmed-harrison-ford-return/}}</ref>。

=== 前期製作 ===
[[File:Denis_Villeneuve,_Ryan_Gosling,_Harrison_Ford,_Ana_de_Armas_&_Sylvia_Hoeks_(35809515700).jpg|right]]。]]
2015年4月16日，[[雷恩·葛斯林|雷恩·葛斯林]]加入參演會談<ref>{{citation | author=Fleming Jr, Mike | title=Ryan Gosling To Star In ‘Blade Runner’ Sequel | work=Deadline | date=2015-04-16 | url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/blade-runner-sequel-ryan-gosling-denis-villenueve-1201411267/ | accessdate=2015-04-16}}</ref>。葛斯林於2015年11月證實他確定演出，透露主要是[[丹尼·維勒納夫|丹尼·維勒納夫]]和[[羅傑·狄金斯|羅傑·狄金斯]]的緣故他才決定參演<ref>{{citation | author=Goldberg, Matt | title=Ryan Gosling Confirms He’s in ‘Blade Runner 2’; Talks Shane Black’s ‘The Nice Guys’ | work=Collider | date=2015-11-16 | url=http://collider.com/ryan-gosling-blade-runner-2-nice-guys/?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=collidersocial | accessdate=2015-11-16}}</ref>。 5月20日，狄金斯被聘為攝影指導<ref>{{citation | author=Geier, Thom | title=‘Blade Runner’ Sequel Hires Roger Deakins as Cinematographer | work=The Wrap | date=2015-05-20 | url=http://www.thewrap.com/blade-runner-sequel-hires-roger-deakins-as-cinematographer/ | accessdate=2015-05-20}}</ref>。正式拍攝定於7月開始，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]負責美國內的發行，而[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]則負責在國際市場的發行<ref>{{citation | author=Jagernauth, Kevin | title=Denis Villeneuve’s ‘Blade Runner 2’ Starring Ryan Gosling & Harrison Ford Officially Starts Filming In July | work=Indiewire | date=2016-01-25 | url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/01/denis-villeneuves-blade-runner-2-starring-ryan-gosling-harrison-ford-officially-starts-filming-in-july-88181/ | accessdate=2016-01-25}}</ref>。2016年2月，宣布上映日為2018年1月12日<ref>{{citation | author=D'Alessandro, Anthony | title=‘Blade Runner’ Sequel To Blast Off On MLK Weekend 2018 | work=Deadline | date=2016-02-18 | url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/blade-runner-2-mlk-weekend-2018-release-date-1201705051/ | accessdate=2016-02-18}}</ref>。在2015年的[[多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]的採訪中，維勒納夫透露，劇情包含主角戴克是否為人或人造人的不確定性<ref>{{citation | author=Eisenberg, Eric | title=Blade Runner 2 Will Take Care Of The Original's Biggest Mystery | work=Cinemablend | date= September 2015 | url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Blade-Runner-2-Take-Care-Original-Biggest-Mystery-82407.html | accessdate=2016-04-28}}</ref>。

2016年3月31日，[[羅蘋·萊特|羅蘋·萊特]]進入參演的最後會談<ref>{{citation | author=Kit, Borys | title=Robin Wright in Final Talks to Join Harrison Ford in 'Blade Runner' Sequel | work=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' | date= 2016-03-31 | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/robin-wright-final-talks-join-879651 | accessdate=2016-03-31}}</ref>，4月2日，[[戴夫·巴帝斯塔|戴夫·巴帝斯塔]]在自己的網站上貼出摺紙的圖樣，暗示自己將會在片中飾演一名角色<ref>{{citation | author=Anderson, Ethan | title=Dave Bautista Likely Bringing Some Muscle to ‘Blade Runner 2’ | work=Slash Film | date=2016-04-02 | url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dave-bautista-joining-blade-runner-2/ | accessdate=2016-04-02}}</ref>。4月4日，萊特和巴帝斯塔確定加入劇組，並打算於2016年7月開拍<ref>{{citation | author=Pedersen, Erik | title=Dave Bautista Joins ‘Blade Runner’ Sequel | work=Deadline | date=2016-04-04 | url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/dave-bautista-blade-runner-sequel-guardians-of-the-galaxy-drax-1201731615/ | accessdate=2016-04-04}}</ref>。2016年4月下旬，該片的上映日改為2017年10月6日<ref>{{citation | author=Kroll, Justin | title=‘Blade Runner’ Sequel Moves to October 2017 | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2016-04-20 | url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/blade-runner-sequel-release-date-changed-1201757777/ | accessdate=2016-04-20}}</ref>，而[[安娜·德哈瑪斯|安娜·德哈瑪斯]]與[[希薇亞·荷克絲|希薇亞·荷克絲]]也將參與演出<ref>{{citation | author=Kroll, Justin | title=‘Blade Runner 2’ Casts ‘Knock Knock’ Star Ana De Armas | work=The Wrap | date=2016-04-21 | url=https://www.thewrap.com/blade-runner-2-casts-knock-knock-star-ana-de-armas/ | accessdate=2016-04-22}}</ref><ref>{{citation | author=Galuppo, Mia | title=Dutch Actress Sylvia Hoeks Joins Cast of 'Blade Runner' | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2016-04-26 | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sylvia-hoeks-joins-blade-runner-887952 | accessdate=2016-04-26}}</ref>。{{link-en|卡菈·尤利|Carla Juri}}於2016年5月加入<ref>{{citation | author=McNary, Dave | title=‘Blade Runner’ Sequel Casts ‘Wetlands’ Star Carla Juri | work=Variety | date=2016-04-26 | url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/blade-runner-sequel-carla-juri-1201771524/ | accessdate=2016-04-26}}</ref>。6月，宣布[[麥坎西·黛維斯|麥坎西·黛維斯]]與[[巴克哈德·阿卜迪|巴克哈德·阿卜迪]]將參演電影<ref>{{citation | author=Kit, Borys | title='Martian' Actress Mackenzie Davis Joins 'Blade Runner' Sequel (Exclusive) | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2016-06-07 | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/martian-actress-mackenzie-davis-joins-874739 | accessdate=2016-06-07}}</ref><ref>{{citation | author=Pedersen, Erik | title=‘Blade Runner’ Sequel Adds ‘Captain Phillips’ Co-Star Barkhad Abdi | work=Deadline | date=2016-06-28 | url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/blade-runner-sequel-barkhad-abdi-cast-1201780866/ | accessdate=2016-06-28}}</ref>，而{{link-en|大衛·達斯馬齊連|David Dastmalchian}}和{{link-en|希安·阿巴斯|Hiam Abbass}}則於7月時加入劇組<ref>[http://variety.com/2016/film/news/blade-runner-sequel-new-cast-members-david-dastmalchian-hiam-abbass-1201813486/ ‘Blade Runner’ Sequel Adds Two New Cast Members]</ref>。維納勒夫原本想讓[[大衛·鮑伊|大衛·鮑伊]]參演，但他在製作開始前過世；[[傑瑞德·雷托|傑瑞德·雷托]]於8月加入演出<ref>[http://variety.com/2016/film/news/jared-leto-blade-runner-sequel-1201840363/ Jared Leto Joins ‘Blade Runner’ Sequel]</ref>。2017年3月，[[愛德華·詹姆斯·歐蒙|愛德華·詹姆斯·歐蒙]]證實，他將回歸演出蓋夫一角，但和前集一樣戲份不多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/blade-runner-2049-casts-edward-james-olmos-986073|title=Edward James Olmos Returning For 'Blade Runner 2049'|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Graeme|last=McMillan|date=2017-03-14|accessdate=2017-03-14}}</ref>。

維勒納夫在接受《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》採訪時透露，電影將設定於前集的幾十年後，電影雖同樣以[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]為背景，但地球的氣候會有所不同，在片中的海洋、雨、雪都是有毒的。後來，雷利·史考特被證實將會擔任監製<ref>[http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/15/blade-runner-sequel-concept-art?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter Blade Runner sequel concept art: See a first look]</ref>。維納勒夫在接受采访时表示北京也作为本片一个重要的设定参考样本，由前作导演[[雷德利·斯科特|雷德利·斯科特]]推荐给他。<ref>[https://weibo.com/1788911247/Fs7X4A3bv? @谷大白话].新浪微博.2017-10-26.[2017-10-26].</ref>

2016年10月，宣布片名定作《銀翼殺手2049》，在此前皆是以《銀翼殺手2》暫稱<ref name="blade runner 2049">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-et-hc-blade-runner-2049-20161006-snap-story.html|title=The 'Blade Runner' sequel finally has a title — 'Blade Runner 2049' — but what does it mean?|first=Mark|last=Olsen|date=2016-10-06|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2016-10-06}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
正式拍攝於2016年7月6日在[[布達佩斯|布達佩斯]]進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BHguM8BDLxW/|title=My heart is racing... Day 1 for #BR !|access-date=2016-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723075334/https://www.instagram.com/p/BHguM8BDLxW/|archive-date=2017-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2016年8月25日，在歐瑞製片廠的一搭景倒塌，使一名建築工人被壓死<ref>[http://mashable.com/2016/08/25/blade-runner-sequel-construction-worker-killed/?utm_cid=mash-com-Tw-main-link#j.LA3Q71sOqc Construction worker killed on set of 'Blade Runner' sequel]</ref>。拍攝於2016年11月在匈牙利結束<ref name="prinpro">{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/blade-runner-2049-will-be-r-rated-confirms-denis-villeneuve/5112413.article#|title='Blade Runner 2049' will be R-rated, confirms Denis Villeneuve|first=Tom|last=Grater|date=2016-12-21|website=Screendaily.com|publisher={{le|Screen International|Screen International|Media Business Insight}}}}</ref>。

=== 後期製作 ===
《銀翼殺手2049》的剪輯工作在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]進行，於2016年12月開始；電影主要以[[美國電影分級制度|R級]]方向製作<ref name="prinpro" />。在2017年的[[聖地牙哥國際動漫展|聖地牙哥國際動漫展]]上，維勒納夫透露，目前電影初剪的片長為2小時半<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/blade-runner-2049-running-time/|title='Blade Runner 2049’ Runtime Revealed by Denis Villeneuve|date=2017-07-21|publisher=|accessdate=2017-07-26}}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
